<%@ page language="java" contentType="text/html; charset=UTF-8" pageEncoding="UTF-8"%>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Spoon - 결제 완료</title>
<style>
    body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; background-color: #f8f9fa; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; height: 100vh; margin: 0; }
    .container { background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); text-align: center; }
    h1 { color: #2ecc71; font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    p { color: #666; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #333; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; }
    .btn:hover { background-color: #555; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>🎉</h1>
        <h2>결제가 완료되었습니다!</h2>
        <p>주문해주셔서 감사합니다. <br> 주문 내역은 마이페이지에서 확인 가능합니다.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn">메인으로 돌아가기</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>